pedalog-interface
-----------------

Interface software by Renewable Energy Innovation for the Pedalog pedal power monitoring device:
http://www.re-innovation.co.uk/index.php

This software should work on any platform for which Mono is available, and libpedalog can be compiled -
although only Debian and Windows have been tested so far.

Debian/Ubuntu
-------------

libpedalog needs to be installed before this program will run. It can be installed using the following
steps:

1) Add the following lines to /etc/apt/sources.list:

deb http://ppa.launchpad.net/powwow-pedal-power/pedalog/ubuntu maverick main 
deb-src http://ppa.launchpad.net/powwow-pedal-power/pedalog/ubuntu maverick main

2) Install dependencies:

sudo apt-get install mono libpedalog

3) Run program!

pedalog-interface
